headline: 5 Must-Read Analyst Questions From Align Technology’s Q4 Earnings Call
summary: Align Technology's fourth quarter was met with a positive market response, as management pointed to strong growth in clear aligner volumes and continued momentum within dental service organizations (DSOs). CEO Joe Hogan highlighted that the improved results were driven by record case volumes in Europe, Latin America, and Asia-Pacific, with DSOs in the Americas delivering double-digit year-over-year growth.
